Package com.collation.platform.model.topology.app.sms

Interface Summary
SMSAdvertizements SMS_Advertisement class is used to announce software package programs that are available for running on clients.
SMSCollectionClients Class is an abstract class.
SMSCollections Collection class contains the rules that logically relate resources into collections of resources.
SMSHierarchy Show a hierarchy of sms cities
SMSPackage SMS_Package class contains information about its programs, such as identifying the source files, how the files are copied to the distribution point, and refresh details.
SMSProgram Class describes a program or command to run when software is distributed to a client computer.
SMSQuery SMS_Query class serves as a container for predefined queries.
SMSReports Report represents a fully defined report that can be run by the SMS Reports.
SMSResource  
SMSServerProcess Name of Windows Serivce Process which is running sms
SMSSiteBoundaries This class will show a boundaries for a site server.
SMSSiteComponents SMS_Components class reports on the health of individual SMS components by counting the error, warning, and informational status messages produced by each component.
SMSSiteServer SMS_Site class contains identification and status data for an SMS site installation.
